里安|優羅斯·里安]]執導第二集。<ref>{{cite press release|publisher= Hartswood Films|date= January 2010|url= http://www.hartswoodfilms.co.uk/pdf/sherlock-start-of-shoot-press-release.pdf|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110716174250/http://www.hartswoodfilms.co.uk/pdf/sherlock-start-of-shoot-press-release.pdf|archivedate= 2011-07-16|format= PDF|title= Filming Begins on 'Sherlock'|accessdate= 2010-01-28|deadurl= yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last= Levine|first= Nick|date= 2010-04-17|url= http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/s7/doctor-who/tubetalk/a214862/mark-gatiss-talks-who-sherlock.html|title= Mark Gatiss talks 'Who', 'Sherlock'|work= Digital Spy|accessdate= 2010-05-28|archive-date= 2017-10-11|archive-url= https://www.webcitation.org/6u8J9IGHv?url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/s7/doctor-who/tubetalk/a214862/mark-gatiss-talks-who-sherlock.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>三集拍攝和播出的順序相反。<ref name="s1ep3-comm"/>

加蒂斯表示他們想「像歷史版本迷戀維多利亞時代的倫敦一樣迷戀現代倫敦」。<ref name="unlocking"/>劇組的大本營設在哈斯伍德电影公司的[[卡迪夫|卡迪夫]]製作單位西哈斯伍德電影公司，該處單位是趁着BBC開發[[卡迪夫灣|卡迪夫灣]]戲劇村之際進駐附近的。<ref>{{cite news|last= Parker|first= Robin|date= 2009-08-20|url= http://www.broadcastnow.co.uk/news/indies/hartswood-set-to-develop-projects-from-welsh-office/5004700.article|title= Hartswood set to develop projects from Welsh office|format= subscription access|work= Broadcast|publisher= Emap Media|accessdate= 2009-08-20|archive-date= 2012-04-05|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120405095945/http://www.broadcastnow.co.uk/news/indies/hartswood-set-to-develop-projects-from-welsh-office/5004700.article|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref name="Upstairs">{{cite web |first=Maggie |last=Brown |url=http://www.thestage.co.uk/features/feature.php/30501/upstairs-downstairs-the-return-of-a-classic |title=Upstairs, Downstairs: The Return of a Classic |work=[[The_Stage|The Stage]] |date=2010-12-03 |accessdate=2011-11-05 |archive-date=2012-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121011203907/http://www.thestage.co.uk/features/2010/12/upstairs-downstairs-the-return-of-a-classic/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>在卡迪夫拍劇比在倫敦更經濟，部分景物與倫敦相當吻合。<ref name="unlocking"/>但是，標誌性的建築物畢竟不能造假，因此劇組亦必須回到首都取景。<ref name="unlocking"/>福爾摩斯和華生的住處[[貝克街221號B|貝克街221號B]]實際場景是[[高爾街_(倫敦)|高爾北街]]（North Gower Street）185號<ref name="londontown">{{Cite journal |url=http://www.londontown.com/LondonBlog/Nelsons/8800/Holmes_sweet_Holmes |title=Holmes sweet Holmes |date=2010-07-26 |publisher=London Town |first=Sadie |last=Nelson |journal=Nelson's Column |accessdate=2010-08-04  |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100803171413/http://londontown.com/LondonBlog/Nelsons/8800/Holmes_sweet_Holmes |archivedate=2010-08-03 }}</ref>，這是由於真正的貝克街交通繁忙<ref name="speedys">{{cite news |title=Sherlock Holmes, and the riddle of the packed sandwich bar |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1303224/Sherlock-Holmes-riddle-packed-sandwich-bar.html |work=Daily Mail |date=2010-08-15 |accessdate=2010-08-16 |archive-date=2012-05-08 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67V8oW44R?url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1303224/Sherlock-Holmes-riddle-packed-sandwich-bar.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而且存在太多標有夏洛克·福爾摩斯的景物<ref name="s1ep3-comm"/>。執行監製[[贝丽尔·弗图|贝丽尔·弗图]]（Beryl Vertue）解釋把福爾摩斯住所設計成現代場景的重要性，但仍要表現他的怪異，認為他不會住在「太城郊」或「太現代」的地方。<ref name="unlocking"/>

試播集的服裝由BAFTA Cymru獎得主雷·霍尔曼（Ray Holman）設計。<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.costume-designer.co.uk/cv/sherlock/|title= Sherlock|publisher= Ray Holman website|accessdate= 2009-07-21|archive-date= 2017-08-05|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170805144529/http://www.costume-designer.co.uk/portfolio-items/sherlock-pilot/|dead-url= no}}</ref>在正式連續劇版中，康柏拜區穿著一件價值£1,000的Belstaff牌外套。<ref name="indep-costume"/>連續劇的服裝設計師萨拉·阿瑟（Sarah Arthur）解述了自己如何塑造偵探的外型：「福爾摩斯對時尚不感興趣，所以我讓他穿著帶有現代特式的古典裝束：窄腳長褲配一件兩鈕貼身上衣。我也設計了一件貼身襯衣配長身外套以配合動作場面——在倫敦的天際線下非常可觀。」<ref name="indep-costume">{{cite news |first1=Paul |last1=Bignell |first2=Rachel |last2=Shields |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/fashion/news/sherlock-chic-fashion-its-elementary-thanks-to-bbc-2046500.html |title=Sherlock chic! Fashion? It's elementary, thanks to BBC |work=The Independent |date=2010-08-08 |accessdate=2010-08-10 |archive-date=2019-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191230230114/https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/fashion/news/sherlock-chic-fashion-its-elementary-thanks-to-bbc-2046500.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

編劇組表示他們不想把故事強行現代化。<ref name="s1ep1-comm"/>創作期間所遇的困難，包括要決定是否保留福爾摩斯住所前門的「221B」門牌。加蒂斯和莫法特稱現代人只會把門牌數字標示於門外，由門鈴聯繫各個單位。但他們認為整個門牌過於深入民心而將其保留。<ref name="s1ep1-comm"/>編劇組也決定讓兩名主角不帶姓氏地直呼對方名字，而不再是傳統的「福爾摩斯」和「華生」。<ref name="s1ep1-comm"/>劇名Sherlock（福爾摩斯的名字）正好表現這項改動。導演保羅·麥桂根也提出把短訊文字浮於畫面，省去了切入手掌提着電話的鏡頭。<ref name="s1ep1-comm"/>

監製們在籌備第二季期間碰上了檔期問題。兩名主角康柏拜區和費里曼參與拍攝2012年電影《[[霍比特人：意外旅程|-{zh-hans:霍比特人：意外旅程;zh-hk:哈比人：不思議之旅;zh-tw:哈比人：意外旅程;}-]]》，另一方面莫法特也要兼顧《[[異世奇人|異世奇人]]》首席編劇的職務。為保償時間不足，《衛報》報導本季會「重現柯南·道爾最為人熟識的三個故事」。<ref name="guard171211"/>加蒂斯表示創作團隊曾就僅用三年時間完成這些故事起過爭執，但莫法特解釋他們反對「好戲留在後頭」。<ref name="guard171211"/>第二季中，福爾摩斯和華生的關係會變得更深厚，而且華生對福爾摩斯的推理的驚奇漸少。在第二集《[[地獄犬_(新世紀福爾摩斯)|地獄犬]]》中，華生將以充當主要偵查者。<ref name="guard171211"/>受第一季來自觀眾和評論界好評的帶動下，劇組在製作第二季時充滿信心。<ref>{{cite web |title='Sherlock' Steven Moffat interview: 'Holmes might not survive' |date=2012-01-11 |first=Morgan |last=Jeffery |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/s129/sherlock/interviews/a359357/sherlock-steven-moffat-interview-holmes-might-not-survive.html |work=Digital Spy |accessdate=2012-01-13 |archive-date=2012-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120113013556/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/s129/sherlock/interviews/a359357/sherlock-steven-moffat-interview-holmes-might-not-survive.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="uncovered">"Sherlock Uncovered", documentary on ''Sherlock'' series 2 DVD/Blu-ray release</ref>

