== 集數 ==
{{main|神探夏洛克集数列表}}
該劇共播出四季，每季皆由3集構成。第一季最初於2010年7至8月在BBC播出，並於同一年10月在[[公共廣播電視公司|PBS]]首播。<ref>{{cite news |title=The Latest Sherlock Hears a 'Who' |url=http://tv.nytimes.com/2010/10/22/arts/television/22sherlock.html |first=Mike |last=Hale |work=The New York Times |date=21 October 2010 |access-date=2 August 2012 |archive-date=12 March 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200312113406/https://www.nytimes.com/2010/10/22/arts/television/22sherlock.html |url-status=live }}</ref>第二季於2012年1月在英國首次播出，之後在5月於美國播出。<ref>{{cite news |title=Holmes and Watson, Back to Bantering |url=http://tv.nytimes.com/2012/05/05/arts/television/sherlock-returns-on-masterpiece-mystery.html |first=Neil |last=Genzlinger |work=The New York Times |date=4 May 2010 |access-date=2 August 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120627235122/http://tv.nytimes.com/2012/05/05/arts/television/sherlock-returns-on-masterpiece-mystery.html |archive-date=27 June 2012 |url-status=live }}</ref>第三季於2014年1月1日在英國首播，並於1月19日在美國首播。該劇已在180個地區播放。<ref name="S5Lang" />特別集於2016年1月1日同時在BBC One和PBS上首播，標誌著該劇首次在英國和美國的同一天播出。<ref name="SpecialAirdate">{{cite web|url=https://www.ew.com/article/2015/10/24/sherlock-date|title=Sherlock finally gets return date, plus new full trailer|last=Hibberd|first=James|work=Entertainment Weekly|date=24 October 2015|access-date=24 October 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151025134601/http://www.ew.com/article/2015/10/24/sherlock-date|archive-date=25 October 2015|url-status=live}}</ref>第四季於2017年1月1日在BBC One和PBS上首播，並於2017年1月15日完結。<ref name="S4Airdates">{{cite web|url=http://www.radiotimes.com/news/2016-12-06/full-schedule-of-sherlock-series-4-air-dates-confirmed|title=Full schedule of Sherlock series 4 air dates confirmed|author=Paul Jones|work=RadioTimes|date=6 December 2016|access-date=6 December 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161206235753/http://www.radiotimes.com/news/2016-12-06/full-schedule-of-sherlock-series-4-air-dates-confirmed|archive-date=6 December 2016|url-status=live}}</ref>
