=== 第一季（2010年） ===
第一集《連環粉紅命案》部分改編自首部福爾摩斯作品《[[血字的研究|血字的研究]]》，由史蒂芬·莫法特編劇，保羅·麥桂根執導。故事講述福爾摩斯和華生相遇，合租倫敦貝克街一個單位，並協助調查一宗連環疑似自殺案。該集在2010年7月25日透過[[BBC_One|BBC One]]和[[BBC_HD|BBC HD]]同步首播。<ref name="guard-ep1-fig">{{cite news |first=Mark |last=Sweney |title=Sherlock Holmes more popular than Tom Cruise |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2010/jul/26/sherlock-holmes-more-viewers-top-gear |work=The Guardian |date=2010-07-26 |accessdate=2010-08-04 |archive-date=2012-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120120055604/http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2010/jul/26/sherlock-holmes-more-viewers-top-gear |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="press">{{cite web |author=BBC Press Office |date=2010-07-08 |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/pressoffice/proginfo/tv/2010/wk30/unplaced.shtml#unplaced_sherlock |title="Network TV BBC Week 30: Unplaced" Press release |accessdate=2010-07-14 |archive-date=2017-10-11 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6u8JvGks0?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/pressoffice/proginfo/tv/2010/wk30/unplaced.shtml#unplaced_sherlock |dead-url=no }}</ref>

第二集《神秘符號》由史蒂芬·湯普森編劇，優羅斯·里安執導，講述福爾摩斯受聘於故友，調查[[倫敦市|倫敦市]]內的一宗銀行劫殺案。该集部分改编自《[[五枚橘籽|五棵橘核]]》。<ref name="guard-ep2-fig">{{cite news |first=Jason |last=Deans |title=Sherlock on the case with 6.4m |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2010/aug/02/sherlock-bbc1-tv-ratings |work=The Guardian |date=2010-08-02 |accessdate=2010-08-03 |archive-date=2012-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120509085322/http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2010/aug/02/sherlock-bbc1-tv-ratings |dead-url=no }}</ref>

季度結局為《解謎遊戲》，反派角色[[詹姆斯·莫里亚蒂教授|吉姆·莫里亞蒂]]首度登場，設計要求福爾摩斯在時限內偵破多宗看似不相連的案件。本集由马克·加蒂斯編劇，麥桂根執導，在劇終福爾摩斯與莫里亞蒂進行生死較量之際故事結束，留下了待下季分曉的懸念。<ref>{{cite news |first=Sam |last=Wollaston |title=TV review: Sherlock |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/tv-and-radio/2010/aug/09/sherlock-benedict-cumberbatch-tv-review |work=The Guardian |accessdate=2011-04-04 |archive-date=2012-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120218224934/http://www.guardian.co.uk/tv-and-radio/2010/aug/09/sherlock-benedict-cumberbatch-tv-review |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 第二季（2012年） ===
《[[連環粉紅命案|連環粉紅命案]]》收視相當高，據報BBC因此希望加拍幾集。<ref>{{cite news |title=BBC 'keen to film more Sherlock' |first=Christian |last=Tobin |date=2010-07-27 |work=Digital Spy |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/s129/sherlock/news/a251236/bbc-keen-to-film-more-sherlock.html |accessdate=2010-07-28 |archive-date=2010-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100727231812/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/s129/sherlock/news/a251236/bbc-keen-to-film-more-sherlock.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2010年8月10日，《新福爾摩斯》將拍第二季的消息得以證實。<ref name="guard-renew">{{Cite news |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2010/aug/10/sherlock-second-series-bbc |title=Sherlock to return for second series |last=Frost |first=Vicky |date=2010-08-10 |work=The Guardian |accessdate=2010-08-10 |archive-date=2012-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120808105709/http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2010/aug/10/sherlock-second-series-bbc |dead-url=no }}</ref>「Kapow! 2011」大會上，加蒂斯確認將被改編的題材，而且第一季的三名編劇將各撰寫一集。<ref name="ign-kapow">{{cite web |first=Leigh |last=Singer |title=Kapow! 11: Ideal Holmes: Mark Gatiss on the new series of Sherlock and Doctor Who |date=2011-04-10 |url=http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/116/1160905p1.html |work=IGN.com |accessdate=2011-04-26 |archive-date=2011-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110413151336/http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/116/1160905p1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>三個獲選故事《[[波希米亞醜聞|波希米亞醜聞]]》、《[[巴斯克維爾的獵犬|巴斯克維爾的獵犬]]》和《[[最後一案|最後一案]]》是其中三個最為人熟悉的故事，加蒂斯解釋選材：「我們得知首播成功後自然會想幹最著名的故事。」<ref name="ign-kapow"/>「問題是怎樣帶出懸念和三個故事的主題，還有夏洛克和約翰的關係的發展。不能回到『你冷酷無情。』『我不在乎。』之類的對白去。你得勇往直前並確保其他角色也有一些經歷。」<ref name="ign-kapow"/>首兩集由保羅·麥桂根再執導演筒，<ref>{{cite news |title=Director's cut: How Hollywood director witnessed real gore for new tv drama |date=2011-03-07 |first=Brian |last=Mciver |url=http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/showbiz/celebrity-interviews/2011/03/07/director-s-cut-how-hollywood-director-witnessed-real-gore-for-new-tv-drama-86908-22972460/ |work=Daily Record |publisher=Scottish Daily Record and Sunday Mail Ltd. |accessdate=2011-04-26 |archive-date=2011-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110324071116/http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/showbiz/celebrity-interviews/2011/03/07/director-s-cut-how-hollywood-director-witnessed-real-gore-for-new-tv-drama-86908-22972460/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>第三集則交由《異世奇人》導演托比·海因斯。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=96fgOz0uDzs|title=Video: Doctor Who at Wondercon 2011 (View from 36:35)|work=YouTube|accessdate=2011-04-20|quote=So what's next for you?" "I'm doing ''Sherlock''.|archive-date=2019-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190824112629/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=96fgOz0uDzs|dead-url=no}}</ref>第二季仍是三集各90分鐘的連續劇，原定於2011年終播出。<ref>{{cite web |title=New commissions and return of Sherlock for BBC One |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/pressoffice/pressreleases/stories/2010/08_august/28/bbcone.shtml |work=BBC Press Office |date=2010-08-28 |accessdate=2011-01-03 |archive-date=2010-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100916083512/http://www.bbc.co.uk/pressoffice/pressreleases/stories/2010/08_august/28/bbcone.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>不過，由於第一季播映完畢後的持續重播，迫使第二季順延至2012年1月。

《贝尔戈维亚丑闻》在2012年1月1日首播，由史蒂芬·莫法特編劇，保羅·麥桂根執導，部分改編自原著《波希米亞醜聞》，講述福爾摩斯受托要從[[艾琳·艾德勒|艾琳·艾德勒]]手上奪回某皇室成員的親密照片，後者是一名擅長從權貴手中竊取機密資料的冷艷女子。<ref>{{cite news |date=2012-01-02 |title=Last Night's TV: Sherlock, BBC 1 |newspaper=The Independent |first=Tom |last=Sutcliffe |authorlink=Tom Sutcliffe (broadcaster) |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/reviews/last-nights-tv-sherlock-bbc-1-6283989.html |accessdate=2012-01-04 |archive-date=2019-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191230224547/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/reviews/last-nights-tv-sherlock-bbc-1-6283989.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

