=== 第三季（2014年）===
在第二季結局播出後，莫法特和加蒂斯雙雙在[[Twitter|Twitter]]上宣布第三季早已和第二季同時獲得預訂。<ref name="bbc20120116">{{cite news |title=Sherlock to return for third series |date=2012-01-16 |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-16573066 |work=BBC News |accessdate=2012-01-16 |archive-date=2012-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120116210344/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-16573066 |dead-url=no }}</ref>《莱辛巴赫坠落》的解答已在攝製第二季期間一同完成。<ref name="missed-clues">{{cite news |first=Stuart |last=Jeffries |title='There is a clue everybody's missed': Sherlock writer Steven Moffat interviewed |work=The Guardian |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/tv-and-radio/2012/jan/20/steven-moffat-sherlock-doctor-who?newsfeed=true |date=2012-01-20 |accessdate=2012-01-21 |archive-date=2012-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120123032302/http://www.guardian.co.uk/tv-and-radio/2012/jan/20/steven-moffat-sherlock-doctor-who?newsfeed=true |dead-url=no }}</ref>執行監製Beryl Vertue在2012年3月確認第三季將在2013年初開始製作，但播出詳情仍有待確認。<ref>{{cite news |title=Early 2013 filming for Sherlock |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/ariel/17350954 |date=2012-03-13 |work=Ariel |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2010-03-13 |archive-date=2012-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120315202937/http://www.bbc.co.uk/ariel/17350954 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Sherlock series three – filming begins early 2013 |url=http://www.radiotimes.com/news/2012-03-13/sherlock-series-three---filming-begins-early-2013 |date=2012-03-13 |work=Radio Times |publisher=Immediate Media Company Limited |accessdate=2010-03-13 |archive-date=2017-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170315061407/http://www.radiotimes.com/news/2012-03-13/sherlock-series-three---filming-begins-early-2013 |dead-url=no }}</ref>莫法特其後宣布第三季在2013年1月開拍。<ref name="moff-sa-ds"/>加蒂斯會為第一集的劇本執筆，該集部分改編自《[[空屋_(福爾摩斯)|空屋]]》（原著中福爾摩斯復生歸來的一集）。<ref>{{cite web |title=Benedict Cumberbatch, Mark Gatiss tease 'Sherlock' future |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/s129/sherlock/news/a384026/benedict-cumberbatch-mark-gatiss-tease-sherlock-future.html |work=Digital Spy |date=2012-05-28 |first=Morgan |last=Jeffery |accessdate=2012-05-28 |archive-date=2012-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120531003124/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/s129/sherlock/news/a384026/benedict-cumberbatch-mark-gatiss-tease-sherlock-future.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>加蒂斯透露會讓華生在重遇福爾摩斯時有不一樣的反應，「我總覺得華生只會以暈倒作反應是不太可能的，相反可能是一口可怕的髒話。」<ref>{{cite news |work=The Telegraph |date=2012-05-03 |title=Sherlock series three: new details revealed |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/9243417/Sherlock-series-three-new-details-revealed.html |accessdate=2012-08-17 |archive-date=2012-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120617044818/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/9243417/Sherlock-series-three-new-details-revealed.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>莫法特和汤普森會一如既往編寫餘下的兩集。<ref name="moff-sa-ds">{{cite web |title=Steven Moffat on 'Doctor Who', 'Sherlock' and his BAFTA Special Award |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/s7/doctor-who/news/a382427/steven-moffat-on-doctor-who-sherlock-and-his-bafta-special-award.html |date=2012-05-19 |work=Digital Spy |first=Morgan |last=Jeffery |accessdate=2012-05-28 |archive-date=2013-07-11 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6I1yn1X5A?url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/s7/doctor-who/news/a382427/steven-moffat-on-doctor-who-sherlock-and-his-bafta-special-award.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

莫法特渴望着手讓華生遷出福爾摩斯的住處，但不肯定會否為他安排一段婚姻。<ref name="ds-moff-trf">{{cite web |title='Sherlock' Steven Moffat interview: 'Holmes might not survive' |date=2012-01-11 |first=Morgan |last=Jeffery |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/s129/sherlock/interviews/a359357/sherlock-steven-moffat-interview-holmes-might-not-survive.html |work=Digital Spy |accessdate=2012-01-13 |archive-date=2012-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120113013556/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/s129/sherlock/interviews/a359357/sherlock-steven-moffat-interview-holmes-might-not-survive.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>莫法特亦希望起用柯南道爾作品中的其他反派和對手。他沒有透露莫里亞蒂有否製造假死，但表示在下季莫里亞蒂不會有很重的戲分。<ref>{{cite news |title=Steven Moffat: expect new Sherlock villains |url=http://www.radiotimes.com/news/2012-03-01/steven-moffat-expect-new-sherlock-villains |date=2012-03-01 |work=Radio Times |publisher=Immediate Media Company Limited |accessdate=2010-03-13 |archive-date=2012-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120303224238/http://www.radiotimes.com/news/2012-03-01/steven-moffat-expect-new-sherlock-villains |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title='Sherlock' creator: 'Moriarty won't return' |url=http://www.nme.com/filmandtv/news/sherlock-creator-moriarty-wont-return/261748 |date=2012-03-02 |work=NME |accessdate=2010-03-13 |archive-date=2012-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120304201201/http://www.nme.com/filmandtv/news/sherlock-creator-moriarty-wont-return/261748 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

莫法特和加蒂斯公布了第三季劇情的三個相關詞：「老鼠、婚禮、弓」（{{lang|en|''rat, wedding, bow''}}）。在2012年8月愛丁堡國際電視節上，莫法特表示三個詞「或許有誤導作用，它們不是標題，只是一些玩笑甚或是線索，但可能是刻意讓人空想一場的計謀。」<ref>{{cite news |first=Vicky |last=Frost |title=Sherlock series three: creators give clues about episodes |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/tv-and-radio/2012/aug/24/sherlock-series-three-episodes |work=The Guardian |date=2012-08-24 |accessdate=2012-08-24 |archive-date=2012-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120824222018/http://www.guardian.co.uk/tv-and-radio/2012/aug/24/sherlock-series-three-episodes |dead-url=no }}</ref>

