1-04 |archive-date=2012-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120113070843/http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/2012/jan/03/sherlock-sexist-steven-moffat?newsfeed=true |dead-url=no }}</ref>但其他評論家和莫法特本人也作出反駁。<ref>{{cite web|first=Laura|last=Pledger|url=http://www.radiotimes.com/news/2012-03-08/ten-strong-tv-women|title=Ten strong TV women|work=[[Radio_Times|Radio Times]]|date=2012-03-08|accessdate=2012-05-05|archive-date=2012-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120420172628/http://www.radiotimes.com/news/2012-03-08/ten-strong-tv-women|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="missed-clue">{{cite news |first=Stuart |last=Jeffries |title='There is a clue everybody's missed': Sherlock writer Steven Moffat interviewed |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/tv-and-radio/2012/jan/20/steven-moffat-sherlock-doctor-who?newsfeed=true |work=The Guardian |location=London |date=2012-01-20 |accessdate=2012-01-21 |archive-date=2012-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120123032302/http://www.guardian.co.uk/tv-and-radio/2012/jan/20/steven-moffat-sherlock-doctor-who?newsfeed=true |dead-url=no }}</ref>季度結局《萊辛巴赫坠落》裏關於福爾摩斯如何偽造自殺的問題，引起了網絡和報章媒體的熱烈討論。<ref name="missed-clue"/>

電視劇的人氣為服裝店帶來意外收益。零售商[[Debenhams|Debenhams]]報告不少人前來購買夏洛克的相關大衣。成衣生產商[[Belstaff|Belstaff]]在第一季結局播出前把班奈狄克·康柏拜區所穿的羊毛大衣重新投入生產。<ref name="petridis">{{cite news |first=Alexis |last=Petridis |authorlink=Alexis Petridis |title=No chic, Sherlock |work=The Guardian |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/lifeandstyle/2010/sep/04/sherlock-fashion-mens-coats |date=2010-09-04 |accessdate=2010-09-07 |archive-date=2011-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111230083859/http://www.guardian.co.uk/lifeandstyle/2010/sep/04/sherlock-fashion-mens-coats |dead-url=no }}</ref>《獨立報》報導，「設計師保罗·科斯特洛（Paul Costelloe）因應需求，提供定製與電視劇相關的大衣和圍巾，同時[[薩佛街|薩佛街]]裁縫约翰·皮尔斯（John Pearse）也稱大量客人前來定製演員們穿的衣服。<ref name="indep-costume"/>記者亚历克西斯·彼得里迪斯（Alexis Petridis）如此評論：「你能理解為何男人都要這個外形。也許他們注意到康柏拜區，即使不是標準的電視英俊猛男，對女性觀眾的作用多大……推測這一定和衣服有關。所以英國最新的男性時尚指標是一個[[無性戀|無性戀]]、反社會、一出場便用馬鞭鞭屍的虛構角色。就連大偵探本人也不會推理到潮流會如此發展。」<ref name="petridis"/>出版商和書店報導第一季播出期間福爾摩斯書籍的銷售量上升180%。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Stone |first1=Philip |first2=Katie |last2=Allen |date=2010-08-12 |archivedate=2010-08-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100815050142/http://www.thebookseller.com/news/125685-no-shit-sherlock-as-tv-adaptation-boosts-book-sales.html |url=http://www.thebookseller.com/news/125685-no-shit-sherlock-as-tv-adaptation-boosts-book-sales.html |title=No shit Sherlock as TV adaptation boosts book sales |publisher=TheBookseller.com |accessdate=2010-08-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>Speedy's，劇中福爾摩斯住所取景地點樓下的三文治店也在熱潮中分一杯羹，它因為路人認得在劇中出現過而吸引到大量新顧客。<ref name="speedys"/>[[BBC_Online|BBC Online]]為劇中的虛構世界設立數個搭配網站，負責構建網站的編劇约瑟夫·利德斯特（Joseph Lidster）也曾為《異世奇人》設計搭配網站。<ref name="tieien">{{cite web |title=Sherlock: Other Sherlock related websites |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/drama/sherlock/disclaimer.shtml |work=BBC Online |accessdate=2010-07-25 |archive-date=2010-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100727143507/http://www.bbc.co.uk/drama/sherlock/disclaimer.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>2012年3月，非官方的愛好者網站Sherlockology當選[[Shorty_Awards|Shorty Awards]]最佳社交媒體愛好者網站。<ref>{{cite news |first=Paul |last=Jones |url=http://www.radiotimes.com/news/2012-04-04/sherlock-fan-site-wins-at-shorty-social-media-awards |title=Sherlock fan site wins at "Shorty" social media awards |work=Radio Times |date=2012-04-04 |accessdate=2012-04-04 |archive-date=2012-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120702120127/http://www.radiotimes.com/news/2012-04-04/sherlock-fan-site-wins-at-shorty-social-media-awards |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |first=Chenda |last=Ngak |title=Shorty Awards honors social media, NASA, Bloomberg |url=http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-501465_162-57405246-501465/shorty-awards-honors-social-media-nasa-bloomberg/ |work=CBS News |date=2012-03-27 |accessdate=2012-04-04 |archive-date=2012-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120505130331/http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-501465_162-57405246-501465/shorty-awards-honors-social-media-nasa-bloomberg |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Sherlock’s survival secret already filmed |first=Nick |last=Ames |date=2012-06-27 |url=http://www.kentnews.co.uk/home/sherlock_s_survival_secret_already_filmed_1_1423528 |work=Kent News |accessdate=2012-07-24 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120630115220/http://www.kentnews.co.uk/home/sherlock_s_survival_secret_already_filmed_1_1423528 |archivedate=2012-06-30 }}</ref>

=== 性向定位爭議 ===

編劇[[馬克·加蒂斯|馬克·加蒂斯]]是已[[出櫃|出櫃]]的[[男同性戀者|男同性戀者]]，且當選過《[[獨立報|獨立報周日]]》評選的英國2010年<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/news/the-iiosi-pink-list-2010-2040472.html|title=The IoS Pink List 2010|publisher=[[The_Independent_on_Sunday|The Independent on Sunday]]|date=2010-08-01|accessdate=2010-08-01|quote=The League of Gentlemen star is set for a bonanza 2010. As well as co-creating the BBC's acclaimed Sherlock Holmes reboot, he'll also be seen in his adaptation of HG Wells' ''First Men in the Moon''. An appearance in an Alan Ackybourn revival at the National Theatre is also mooted.|location=London|archive-date=2010-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100802052109/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/news/the-iiosi-pink-list-2010-2040472.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>和2011年<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/news/the-iiosi-pink-list-2011-2374595.html | title=The IoS Pink List 2011 | location=London | work=The Independent | first=Ian | last=Herbert | date=2011-10-23 | accessdate=2012-08-10 | archive-date=2011-10-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111025211852/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/news/the-iiosi-pink-list-2011-2374595.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>最有影響力的同性戀者，並和該劇中的演員Ian Hallard有[[英國民事伴侶關係|民事伴侶關係]]<ref name="Scot interview">{{cite web |last=Randall |first=Lee |url=http://thescotsman.scotsman.com/features/The-Monday-Interview-Mark-Gatiss.4699282.jp |title=The Monday Interview: Mark Gatiss - Top of the League - The Scotsman |publisher=Thescotsman.scotsman.com |date=2008-11-17 |accessdate=2010-10-28 |quote=Amid all this activity, Gatiss found time, last spring, to get married. He and Ian have been together for nearly a decade... He and Ian are the devoted 'parents' of Bunsen, a Labrador retriever. |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101126135101/http://thescotsman.scotsman.com/features/The-Monday-Interview-Mark-Gatiss.4699282.jp |archive-date=2010-11-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。
有評論認為，電視劇中的一些情節亦在暗示[[夏洛克·福爾摩斯|福爾摩斯]]與[[約翰·華生|華生]]的[[同性戀|同性戀]]關係，例如他們搬進貝克街的公寓後，房東哈德遜夫人認為他們是一起的，對他們說「如果你們需要一間的話，樓上還有一間臥室。」（There's another bedroom upstairs… that is if you'll be needing one.），以及他們去餐館吃飯時，餐館老闆說「夏洛克，菜單上所有的東西你和你的情人都可以點。我去拿支蠟燭擺在桌子上，這樣更浪漫些。」 （Sherlock, anything on the menu, free, for you and your date. I'll get a candle for the table. It's more romantic.）。華生和福爾摩斯亦一度認為對方是同性戀，華生問福爾摩斯：「你有男朋友嗎？有的話也沒關係。」（Do you have a boyfriend? which is fine by the way.）福爾摩斯回答他：「我已經和工作結婚了，不過知道你喜歡我我挺高興的。」（I consider myself married to my work but I am flattered you like me.）

然而這些情節卻引發了一些[[福爾摩斯探案|福爾摩斯]]原著書迷們的惱火，而編劇[[馬克·加蒂斯|馬克·加蒂斯]]回應稱不喜歡對於觀眾也沒有很大影響，[[夏洛克·福爾摩斯|夏洛克·福爾摩斯]]是總被搬上-{zh-tw:螢幕;zh-cn:屏幕}-的人物，總會有下一個出來，另一編劇[[史蒂芬·莫法特|史蒂芬·莫法特]]則稱[[福爾摩斯_(2009年電影)|2009年的電影版本]]同性戀傾向更為嚴重。而福爾摩斯小說愛好者、曾舉辦偵探小說書展的Peter Stewart則表示不喜歡夏洛克有同性戀傾向這個說法，並稱這並不是[[阿瑟·柯南·道爾|阿瑟·柯南·道爾]]爵士的構思。<ref>{{cite news|author=Peter Dyke|title=BBC's Sherlock Holmes gay subtext sparks fan fury|url=http://www.dailystar.co.uk/posts/view/145718/BBC-s-Sherlock-Holmes-gay-subtext-sparks-fan-fury/|accessdate=2012-08-09|newspaper=Daily Star|date=2010-07-23|archive-date=2011-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110421034855/http://www.dailystar.co.uk/posts/view/145718/BBC-s-Sherlock-Holmes-gay-subtext-sparks-fan-fury/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

