第一季[[DVD|DVD]]和[[Blu-ray|Blu-ray]]由[[2entertain|2entertain]]分別於2010年8月30日在[[英國|英國]]，11月4日在[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]，<ref>{{cite web |title=Sherlock DVD release date Australia |url=http://www.jbhifionline.com.au/dvd/dvd-genres/drama-romance/sherlock/579134 |work=JBHIFI |date=2010-10-10 |accessdate=2010-10-19 |archive-date=2011-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111206074742/http://www.jbhifionline.com.au/dvd/dvd-genres/drama-romance/sherlock/579134 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2010年11月9日在[[美國|美國]]發行。DVD收錄全季三集和特別花絮。《連環粉紅命案》由史蒂芬·莫法特，马克·加蒂斯和蘇惟周評述，《解謎遊戲》則有班奈狄克·康柏拜區，馬丁·費里曼和马克·加蒂斯。由Coky Giedroyc執導，未播出的60分鐘版試播集《連環粉紅命案》也收錄其中。<ref>''Sherlock'' DVD, Catalogue number: BBCDVD3223</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Sherlock DVD review |first=Stu |last=Anderson |work=Den of Geek |url=http://www.denofgeek.com/Reviews/581560/sherlock_dvd_review.html |date=2010-09-01 |accessdate=2010-09-07 |archive-date=2012-05-08 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67V3vBMlV?url=http://www.denofgeek.com/Reviews/581560/sherlock_dvd_review.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>評論家Mark Lawson稱此舉「勇氣可嘉」。<ref name="lawson-rebirth"/>British Board of Film Classification把試播集和其外三集評級為12（12歲以下人士不得租借或購買）。<ref name="bbfc-pilot">{{cite web |title=SHERLOCK – A Study in Pink (pilot) |url=http://www.bbfc.co.uk/AVV271177 |work=BBFC |date=2010-07-23 |accessdate=2010-07-26 |archive-date=2010-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100804195953/http://www.bbfc.co.uk/AVV271177 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=SHERLOCK – A Study in Pink |url=http://www.bbfc.co.uk/AVV271691 |work=BBFC |date=2010-08-02 |accessdate=2010-08-05 |archive-date=2012-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120415013328/http://www.bbfc.co.uk/AVV271691/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=SHERLOCK – The Blind Banker |url=http://www.bbfc.co.uk/AVV271625 |work=BBFC |date=2010-08-02 |accessdate=2010-08-05 |archive-date=2012-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120415013443/http://www.bbfc.co.uk/AVV271625/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=SHERLOCK – The Great Game |url=http://www.bbfc.co.uk/AVV271626 |work=BBFC |date=2010-08-02 |accessdate=2010-08-05 |archive-date=2012-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120415013520/http://www.bbfc.co.uk/AVV271626/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>DVD還收錄一段32分鐘製作花絮《Unlocking Sherlock》。<ref>{{cite web |title=Unlocking Sherlock |url=http://www.bbfc.co.uk/AVV271627 |work=BBFC |date=2010-08-02 |accessdate=2010-08-05 |archive-date=2011-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110119205846/http://www.bbfc.co.uk/AVV271627 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

第二季的影碟於2012年1月23日在英國發行，<ref>{{cite web |title=BBC's Sherlock Will Return For Series 3 |url=http://www.cinemablend.com/television/BBC-Sherlock-Return-Series-3-38659.html |first=Jesse |last=Carp |date=2012-01-16 |work=Cinema Blend |accessdate=2012-01-28 |archive-date=2019-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190812182203/https://www.cinemablend.com/television/BBC-Sherlock-Return-Series-3-38659.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>特別花絮包括《貝爾戈維亞醜聞》和《巴斯克維爾獵犬》的評述和紀錄片《Sherlock Uncovered》。<ref>{{cite web |title=Sherlock – the hounds of baskerville |url=http://www.bbfc.co.uk/BVV286085/ |work=British Board of Film Classification |date=2011-12-20 |accessdate=2012-01-08 |archive-date=2020-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200312113544/https://bbfc.co.uk/releases/sherlock-hounds-baskerville-video |dead-url=no }}</ref>其後，Silva Screen分在2012年1月30日和2月27日發布首兩季的原聲帶專輯。<ref name=soundtrack.series1>{{cite web |title=Sherlock |url=http://www.silvascreen.com/index.php/2011/12/14/sherlock/ |work=Silva Screen Records |accessdate=2012-01-14 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120113074859/http://www.silvascreen.com/index.php/2011/12/14/sherlock/ |archivedate=2012-01-13 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=More Sherlock Music On The Way |url=http://www.silvascreen.com/index.php/2012/01/20/more-sherlock-music-on-the-way/ |date=2012-01-20 |work=Silva Screen Records |accessdate=2012-03-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120424070313/http://www.silvascreen.com/index.php/2012/01/20/more-sherlock-music-on-the-way/ |archivedate=2012-04-24 }}</ref>

BBC Books也為柯南·道爾的原著小說出版[[商業搭配|搭配]]版本，封面為兩名演員康柏拜區和費里曼的劇照。2011年秋季發行的《[[血字的研究|血字的研究]]》和《[[福爾摩斯辦案記|福爾摩斯辦案記]]》分別附有莫法特和加蒂斯寫的序言。<ref name="moff-study"/><ref>{{cite book |title=Sherlock – [[The_Adventures_of_Sherlock_Holmes|The Adventures of Sherlock Holmes]] |first=Arthur |last=Conan Doyle |year=2011 |publisher=BBC Books |isbn=1-84990-367-0 |origyear=First published 1892}}</ref>2012年3月發行的《[[巴斯克維爾的獵犬|巴斯克維爾的獵犬]]》、《[[四签名|四签名]]》和《[[福爾摩斯回憶錄|福爾摩斯回憶錄]]》分別由康柏拜區、費里曼和湯普森寫序。<ref>{{cite book |title=Sherlock – [[The_Hound_of_the_Baskervilles|The Hound of the Baskervilles]] |first=Arthur |last=Conan Doyle |publisher=BBC Books |year=2012 |origyear=First published 1902|isbn=1-84990-409-X}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |title=Sherlock – Sign of Four |first=Arthur |last=Conan Doyle |publisher=BBC Books |year=2012 |isbn=1-84990-404-9|origyear=First published 1890}}</ref><ref name="memoirs"/>根據《[[廣播時報|廣播時報]]》报-{道}-，《新福爾摩斯》的成功使得柯南·道爾的原著作品再度熱賣。<ref>{{cite news |first=Paul |last=Jones |title=Benedict Cumberbatch's Sherlock boosts Conan Doyle book sales |url=http://www.radiotimes.com/news/2012-01-17/benedict-cumberbatch%27s-sherlock-boosts-conan-doyle-book-sales |work=Radio Times |date=2012-01-17 |accessdate=2012-01-24 |archive-date=2012-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120118102747/http://www.radiotimes.com/news/2012-01-17/benedict-cumberbatch%27s-sherlock-boosts-conan-doyle-book-sales |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

